title: Keeping Up with Your Goals | Starting the New Year Right

description:
The Gals on the Go offer up expert tips on how to not only make goals, but stick to them, too. But first, the two discuss their highlights & lowlights of the week, how to combat loneliness, and give a quick recap of their very different but very wonderful NYE!
